# Keep the website image build context small + reproducible. The website
# Dockerfile COPYs only the sources it needs; everything below is noise that
# would otherwise be shipped to the daemon (slow) or leak into a layer.
.git
**/node_modules
.venv
venv
**/dist
**/.astro
**/__pycache__
*.pyc
.pytest_cache
.mypy_cache
.ruff_cache
htmlcov
reports
**/.history
build
*.egg-info
